<h2>Introduction...</h2>

<p>We invite the visitors of this site to watch the video of <b>Purohit Technique Of Vaginal Hysterectomy and 
   Salpingo-oophorectomy </b><b>free of cost.</b></p><br>
<p>Kindly refer to the article published in <b>BJOG (British Journal of Obstetrics and Gynaecology), </b>
   an International Journal of Obstetrics and Gynaecology,2003 Dec, Vol. 110 (12) pp.1115-1119 or 
   <a href=#reference>Click Here</a> before 
   watching the <a href="video/showvideo.php">video</a> of about 32 minutes duration.</p><br>
<p>This technique has been innovated by <b>Dr. R. K.Purohit M.D, Director, Department of Obstetrics &amp; Gynaecology,          Purohit General Hospital</b>. By now it has been a well-tried and useful technique at Purohit General Hospital.Many gynaecologic surgeons have been trained by <a href="courses.php"> hands on training</a>.To know more about this technique, click <a href="whyuseful.php">Why This Technique Is Useful</a>.
  <a href="Learn1.php">
  Learn the technique step by step here</a>.</p><br>
<p>To watch the video, kindly <a href="login/register-form.php">Register</a>
    and note the <b>Username</b> &amp; <b>Password</b>.</p><br>
    
<p>Kindly see some <a href="specimen_pictures.php">interesting specimens</a> removed during 
   vaginal hysterectomy by Purohit technique.</p><br>
